overview: Dino has a secret. He appears to be almost average to outsiders, but inside his head, all he thinks about is head and anal action. And everything else in between. And given the choice, he'd rather watch than play. Everything turns sexual with this visualizing voyeur, from a car wash to a laundry run, to walking the dog... and the results are as hilarious as Jim Stell's last AAA video venture, Rescue 69-11. Take a head trip -- inside Dino's head. And if you think there's a hotter place to be, Dream on...
title: Dino Dreams On
